@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_orwfbj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.59) + v2))
    v0 = (v0 * 0.81)
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.18 - v0 + 0.57)) - (tmp / (v1 + 0.20 - v0 + 0.65)))
    data[tid] = v0
